des:
Now you can use Alexa to control all yourSmarthome devices! You can turn on/offyour camera simply by giving orders toAlexa. Alexa can show you the stream fromsupported devices. 
Here's a step by step guide:
(1).Download our "3-link" app in Google Play or iOS App Store;
(2).Launch the app and register a new account(or login if you're already registered);
(3).Turn on 3-link devices and connect them with "3-link" app;
(4).You can rename the devices with3-link App. So if you rename a camera "bedroom cam",then Echo will get that same name after discovered the devices in Step 9:
(5).Download Amazon "Alexa" app from AmazonMarket, Google Play or iOS App Store, and connect Echo with "Alexa" app;
(6).Search the Alexa Skills directory for "3-link"
(7).Click Enable skill of "3-link", then input your account username, password ;
(8).Talk to Echo ""Alexa,discover devices.". Wait till Echo says "Discover is completed".
(9).Now all setup is done. Try talk to Echo to control your devices
Here are the voice commands 3-link has:
“Alexa, show me the camera”
